{"tid":1926522,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"沖san扮香港人大起底2.0","createTime":"2020-03-15T07:31:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T07:02:54.000Z","uid":11368,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d49548922841d6d1878177933e18b4e04152ecba","tid":1926522,"uid":11368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:31:40.000Z","msg":"上次我哋就係老豆揾囝到踢爆沖San呢條偽理性的藍絲KOL，今次就係有新料再爆俾大家食花生。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/03/15/QIeho0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F03%2F15%2FQIeho0.jpg&h=2e0ae367&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/03/15/43fXaY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F03%2F15%2F43fXaY.jpg&h=05dc6784&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/03/15/xGqoZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F03%2F15%2FxGqoZQ.jpg&h=77c4f8ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/03/15/eMfvix.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F03%2F15%2FeMfvix.jpg&h=c32b2829&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/03/15/S8vgFa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F03%2F15%2FS8vgFa.jpg&h=8078a550&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n父親:鍾永強，母親:Grace Leong<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/03/15/BkVK0h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F03%2F15%2FBkVK0h.jpg&h=ed079f0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/03/15/WpV2LF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F03%2F15%2FWpV2LF.jpg&h=c9922dc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n妹妹: Chark Chong<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/03/15/vEIBVn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F03%2F15%2FvEIBVn.jpg&h=f3cafa3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSOURCE - 阿囝搵老豆老母<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事蹟<br />\n<br />\n8)被人踢爆之前係Facebook 成日Po自己做GYM同Workout的Video。又會將自己隻勞力士放上網曬命。好明顯係一個Attention Seeking的人。<br />\n<br />\n9)有連登仔踢爆佢係中學時期已經俾人感覺係Seven下Seven下，最後讀唔掂要轉校。其佢係澳洲讀書時都俾人印象係一個Seven Head！<br />\n<br />\n10)當年係澳洲澳門學生聯會寫文話為左報答父母，而決定唔去申請澳洲居留身分。實情係當年係澳洲攞居留，IELTS無7分或8分，仲要符合澳洲的移民政策先可以成功申請。最諷刺係自己篇文到又寫澳洲人歧視亞洲人，自己多同華人玩。呢種人根本就係垃圾蝗蟲。<br />\n<br />\n11)多次講到自己好愛國，話係國家政策配合下要抵抗外敵？但自己公司係幫Levi&rsquo;s，Disel, Calvin Klein等西方勢力的公司做生意，呢啲人根本係一個機會主義者。<br />\n<br />\n12)支持香港警察，仲要整埋影片「致香港警察的表揚信」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DnY2jRkrlsw&amp;t=30s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDnY2jRkrlsw%26t%3D30s&d=%2BoN05yFcfnwTDzsdE0HOySwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=502224b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DnY2jRkrlsw&amp;t=30s</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個人資料:<br />\n姓名：Odin Chong 鍾志亨<br />\n職業 / 身份：澳門親中人士、澳門慈幼校友會理事、寶發紡織服飾市場擴展經理、廣州市工商聯（總商會）澳門區執委、澳門廠商聯合會青年委員會常務委員<br />\n電話號碼：+852 65148479<br />\n地址：澳門氹仔大連街至尊花城第三座麗閣42L，香港將軍澳和明苑 和暉閣 2306室<br />\n室<br />\n父母：父親 鍾永強，母親 Grace Leong 妹妹 Chark Chong<br />\n學校：大學-澳洲 Griffith University （學士）、University of Queensland (碩士)<br />\n中學：澳門利馬竇中學、澳門慈幼中學、聖若瑟教區中學、澳洲Millennium Secondary School<br />\nFacebook：Odin Chong<br />\nInstagram：Odin0321<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n扮香港人嘅藍絲KOL沖SAN大起底!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1898194/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1898194/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"5409c6fea0e7e0052b5a548e9ea151f506d980b0","tid":1926522,"uid":11368,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T07:32:19.000Z","msg":"再提提大家佢之前威水事蹟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事蹟:<br />\n1）澳門人喺澳洲留過學，但偏偏條條片扮香港人同藍絲飛機，為反送中期間爆紅藍絲Youtuber，以前開箱打機片無人睇，轉講反智藍絲內容卻贏得瀏覽量。<br />\n<br />\n2）入晒廣州市工商聯（總商會）。身為靠大陸生意嘅人，在大陸肛門設廠搞製衣紡織生意，言論咁維穩好難唔係利益所在。<br />\n<br />\n3）同華記正能量、何志光、黑超哥、大波man等成立男人幫大聯盟 (藍絲CHANNEL)，痴痴呆呆坐埋一枱。<br />\n<br />\n4) 鍾意溝女又花心，係一腳踏兩船的Hi Hi，以前係澳洲讀書有個正室係一個城市，同時喺另一個城市同一個女仔出雙入對。<br />\n<br />\n5) 當年係澳洲澳門學生會就煽動學生會集體辭職，迫總會長妥協，結果衰左被人玩返轉頭，被人罵係搞事始祖。哩種人enjoy搞事出風頭，黃定藍對佢嚟講其實無所謂。<br />\n<br />\n6) 澳洲生活咁耐，身為澳門人，但澳洲澳門社會或生活事都少提，更可證明條友係目的導向，一切言論為名為利。<br />\n<br />\n7) 習慣歪理當真理，愚昧廣大藍絲，無時事常識發放不實言論，論點例如:支持香港立23條,認為立左對香港好，可以拉左大台，話隔離埠立左之後風調雨順。聲稱大頭奶粉的官員被拉,實情係劉慶強係05年升任做安徽環保局局長，另外話愛爾蘭係咪痴住英國係要搞獨立嗰個地方，實情愛爾蘭係獨立國家，想搞獨立係蘇格蘭同北愛爾蘭。<br />\n<br />\nSOURCE - 阿囝搵老豆老母<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------<br />\n精選傻的嗎片包括:<br />\n※言論偷換概念，混淆試聽抹黑香港醫護罷工。<br />\n〔中文字幕〕香港三大現狀：口罩之爭、盲搶炎、還有⋯⋯｜沖出黎講＂<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7j9hw7uVQWU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7j9hw7uVQWU&d=%2BoN05yFcfnwTDzsdE0HOySwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=a76d9dc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7j9hw7uVQWU</a><br />\n<br />\n※抺黑勇武行動和歪曲和理非<br />\n〔中文字幕〕澳門一誠VS香港林鄭｜沖出黎講<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JfaPr6z51SM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJfaPr6z51SM&d=%2BoN05yFcfnwTDzsdE0HOySwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=bda49133\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JfaPr6z51SM</a><br />\n<br />\n※批評封關但被連登仔KO,仲要封留言<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1858920/page/11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1858920/page/11</a><br />\n<br />\n※美化中共的經濟發展,但無講到往幾十年的道德敗壞，積極內鬥同利用一帶一路的新殖民主義<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCsGqE-IVUCwyyi_WRsvVLJg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCsGqE-IVUCwyyi_WRsvVLJg&d=%2BoN05yFcfnwTDzsdE0HOySwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=46548e06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCsGqE-IVUCwyyi_WRsvVLJg</a>"},{"pid":"16bb5e7e334508e47c86339adc8